tplConfig.notes: When approaching the Albertsons store, call 623-249-8664 and provide order ID & name before entering store. When you arrive at the store, a mask and self-administered health screening are required. Please get a shopping cart, use the sanitizer station at the front door to wipe the cart and go straight inside to the customer service desk (next to cash registers) maintaining 6-feet social distancing and let an employee know you're there for a 3rd Party Partner delivery order.
